lyrics:
[Verse]
Bheed mein tanha, dil mein dard
Khojta hai sukoon, koi raah sath saath
Jeevan ki dagar, bhari hai raat
Kho gaya hoon khud se, kyun na pata

[Chorus]
Kho gaya hoon khud se, kyun na pata
Dil ki tadap, ab kaise sataye
Bheed mein tanha, dil mein dard
Khojta hai sukoon, koi raah sath saath
